{
"#name"
:
{
"claw"
:
null
,
"cn"
:
"x-cmd AI 消息机器人"
,
"en"
:
"x-cmd AI message bot"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x claw <SUBCMD>"
:
null
}
]
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"自托管 AI Agent 网关，将 LLM 接入微信、飞书、Telegram 等即时通讯平台。\n监听 IM 消息并触发本地 AI Agent 执行自主任务，支持通过 `x agent request` 调用\nclaude, codex, cursor, gemini-cli, opencode, kimi-cli 等多种 AI 引擎，\n每个会话拥有独立 workspace 与持久化上下文记忆。\n"
,
"en"
:
"A self-hosted AI Agent gateway that connects LLMs to WeChat, Feishu, Telegram and other IM platforms.\nListens for IM messages and triggers local AI Agents to execute autonomous tasks,\nsupporting multiple AI engines via `x agent request` (claude, codex, cursor, gemini-cli, opencode, kimi-cli),\nwith independent workspaces and persistent context memory per session.\n"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"使用 'x claw start' 启动网关服务，支持多平台同时运行（如 `x claw start --weixin --telegram`）。\n不指定平台时自动检测已登录的 IM 平台，默认回退到 weixin。\n支持的 IM 平台: weixin, telegram, feishu, qywx。\nAI Agent 引擎可通过 'x agent request' 配置切换（如 claude, codex, cursor, gemini-cli, opencode, kimi-cli）。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Use 'x claw start' to start the gateway, supports multiple platforms simultaneously (e.g., `x claw start --weixin --telegram`).\nAuto-detects logged-in IM platforms when not specified, with weixin as fallback default.\nSupported IM platforms: weixin, telegram, feishu, qywx.\nAI Agent engine can be switched via 'x agent request' config (e.g. claude, codex, cursor, gemini-cli, opencode, kimi-cli).\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw start"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 启动网关服务（自动检测可用平台）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Start gateway service (auto-detect available platform)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw log"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 查看网关服务日志"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Show gateway service log"
}
]
,
